OOC: Dachande, Vulois DID respond to them!  I posted it three times!  You are 
the one not responding! Vulois explained to Dachande and Battera his new 
plan.  He was going to return to the peace talks, but this time they'd all go 
together to prevent mishaps.  He asked if they accepted.  Please respond to 
me. I really want this to work out.

:::Starscream/Sideswipe/Torca/Ratchet/Falcon/Snare/The Destrocons:::
 
::Starscream follows suit, arming his guns and aiming them at the bush::
~~~~~
::Sideswipe grins from ear to ear as he is finally able to see his opponent.  
The smile immeadiatly disapeers from his face as he gets hit by the missle.  
he fires 2 missles and 25 shots at Double Punch::
~~~~~
::Torca was hit by the missle, and gets hit by 2 stinger missles.  He fired 9 
nails at Double Punch, 8 at Injector, and 8 at Bumblebee::
~~~~~
::Ratchet was hit by 2 ion disks in the foot and 1 in the chest.  he 
transformed into beast mode, which had all the weapon benefits of robot mode, 
only with better armor.  He raised his tusks and flapped open his ears, and 
fired 15 shots from each gun and 2 tusk missles at Manterror::
~~~~~
::My Destrons hear Shredder's order.  they were releived, because if they 
waited any longer the ship would prbably be collapsing around them!::
Ramjet: ya dont have to tell me twice!
::They transform into beast and vehicle modes and fly after Shredder::

--part1_c1.a11fe3a.27758c14_boundary
